The evidence with the title 'Best Governors ' says May 5, 2015  ... In introducing Huckabee at the campaign launch , Asa Hutchinson mentioned this TIME list of the best governors in America.  ... Asa Hutchinson listed this as one of Huckabee 's credentials: when Huckabee himself was the top politician in Arkansas, TIME named him one of the country's best governors. 
